  "reference_number": "INU0233",
  "remarks": "\nGhorb Nooh is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Ghorb Nooh is or has been responsible for, engaged in, provided support for, or promoted, or facilitated, a relevant nuclear activity, specifically the proliferation or development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran, or an activity that could lead to the development of nuclear weapons in, or for use in, Iran.",
